### USUARIOS ###
################

### Get All Users (solo admin)
GET {{host}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get User by ID
GET {{host}}/api/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Register
POST {{host}}/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Test User",
    "email": "test@inventario.com",
    "password": "Test1234!",
    "role": "user"
}

### Login
POST {{host}}/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@admin.com",
    "password": "password"
}

### Update User
PUT {{host}}/api/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Admin Actualizado"
}

### Delete User (soft delete - solo admin)
DELETE {{host}}/api/users/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


