########################
### TRANSACCIONES    ###
########################

### Create Transaction OUT (sacar producto)
POST {{host}}/api/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productId": 1,
    "type": "OUT",
    "quantity": 1,
    "notes": "Préstamo para rodaje"
}

### Create Transaction IN (devolver producto)
POST {{host}}/api/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productId": 1,
    "type": "IN",
    "quantity": 1,
    "notes": "Devolución tras rodaje"
}

### Get All Transactions
GET {{host}}/api/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Products OUT by User
GET {{host}}/api/transactions/user/1/out
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Products OUT de otros usuarios
GET {{host}}/api/transactions/others/out
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
